1
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:13,340
Eternal Love of Dream

2
00:02:14,180 --> 00:02:16,620
Episode 28

3
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:26,940
Your Majesty,

4
00:02:28,420 --> 00:02:30,460
has the war of Mount Fuyu not finished yet?

5
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:33,020
That Demon Lord Yan

6
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:34,980
is not a threat.

7
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:36,260
Now that the disaster is quelled,

8
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,220
Your Majesty, why are you still so worried?

9
00:02:39,540 --> 00:02:40,900
I left her in the Fanyin Valley.

10
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:43,580
What have you left?

11
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:45,220
A silk handkerchief.

12
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:49,300
Leave me alone.

13
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:50,540
Yes.

14
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:06,660
Which man in the world

15
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:08,140
doesn't like Ji Heng?

16
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:13,340
In that case,

17
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,580
since His Majesty likes Ji Heng so much,

18
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:16,940
why did I hear that

19
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:19,100
when they got out of the Ten-evil Lotus Land,

20
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:20,740
Ji Heng asked His Majesty for a spiritual fox

21
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:22,220
they found together,

22
00:03:22,540 --> 00:03:24,180
but His Majesty didn't give it to her?

23
00:03:25,140 --> 00:03:26,100
What do you know?

24
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:27,700
It's a strategy.

25
00:03:28,180 --> 00:03:29,380
It's just like you like ice face,

26
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:31,780
so you will try every means to connect with him.

27
00:03:33,980 --> 00:03:35,860
He didn't give that spiritual fox

28
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:36,980
to Ji Heng

29
00:03:37,100 --> 00:03:38,380
so that Ji Heng would visit Tai Chen Palace

30
00:03:38,420 --> 00:03:40,420
frequently to see it later.

31
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:42,860
He's really cunning.

32
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:46,460
Though he talks casually,

33
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:48,300
he's pretty scrupulous.

34
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:51,940
I know you like him,

35
00:03:52,220 --> 00:03:53,740
just as I like Ji Heng.

36
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:55,660
We have the same misfortune.

37
00:03:55,940 --> 00:03:56,740
Take my advice.

38
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,740
It's never too late to mend your ways.

39
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:03,100
I don't know this sentence

40
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:04,380
can also be interpreted this way.

41
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:06,980
Just mend your ways.

42
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:11,260
However, the ice face failed to get married in the end.

43
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:12,420
Ji Heng ran away from the wedding.

44
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,700
He lost not only his empress

45
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:15,900
but also the spiritual fox.

46
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:18,580
How miserable he was!

47
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:25,580
You said you're from Qingqiu.

48
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:26,820
Do you know

49
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:27,900
where that spiritual fox is now?

50
00:04:30,180 --> 00:04:31,420
It sounds ridiculous.

51
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:33,820
The ice face actually

52
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:34,900
came to me for the fox.

53
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:36,940
He thought I had abducted the fox.

54
00:04:37,220 --> 00:04:38,660
Do I look like someone

55
00:04:38,660 --> 00:04:39,620
who would abduct a fox?

56
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,260
He really underestimated me!

57
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:42,940
However,

58
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:45,540
I heard that he still hasn't found it after years of searching.

59
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:47,420
In my opinion,

60
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:49,820
that fox is probably dead.

61
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:52,700
I wonder what kind of a fox that is

62
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:54,260
to be so favored by him.

63
00:04:56,180 --> 00:04:57,300
Warrior Yan,

64
00:04:57,780 --> 00:04:58,660
after talking for so long,

65
00:04:58,780 --> 00:04:59,940
you must be thirsty.

66
00:05:00,420 --> 00:05:01,980
Shall we look for the exit?

67
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:03,300
We can't stay here

68
00:05:03,380 --> 00:05:04,420
forever.

69
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:06,620
You've made a point.

70
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:33,740
Watch out!

71
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:41,380
After all, we've been through trouble together.

72
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:42,500
I can't watch you fall down

73
00:05:42,540 --> 00:05:43,380
and do nothing.

74
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:44,420
Forget it! I'm coming!

75
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:05,140
Today is really an auspicious day.

76
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:06,980
It's exceptionally easy to avoid those spies

77
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:08,100
in the imperial palace and get outside.

78
00:06:13,900 --> 00:06:14,180
Let's go and have a look!

79
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:14,700
What's wrong?

80
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:15,220
Look over there!

81
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:16,980
Turn them over!

82
00:06:21,420 --> 00:06:22,220
They hit someone.

83
00:06:26,580 --> 00:06:27,220
Second Prince!

84
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,700
I pay respects to Your Highness!

85
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,020
How dare you!

86
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:42,180
You actually attacked
the Second Prince of the inseparable king bird!

87
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:43,900
I'm so unlucky

88
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:46,260
to have fallen into the nest of the inseparable king birds!

89
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:49,100
The inseparable king birds had a problem with Qingqiu.

90
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:50,180
I can't let them know

91
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:51,260
I'm from Qingqiu.

92
00:06:59,740 --> 00:07:02,860
It seems that without suffering,

93
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:04,260
you won't know

94
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:06,100
how powerful we inseparable king birds are.

95
00:07:06,660 --> 00:07:07,100
Guards!

96
00:07:07,420 --> 00:07:08,260
Take them to the prison

97
00:07:08,460 --> 00:07:09,180
to wait for execution!

98
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:10,220
- Yes! - Yes!

99
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:14,940
Go!

100
00:07:19,780 --> 00:07:21,860
That girl

101
00:07:21,980 --> 00:07:23,620
looks familiar.

102
00:07:42,740 --> 00:07:45,300
Brother, you finally wake up!

103
00:07:45,940 --> 00:07:47,420
You freaked me out.

104
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:54,580
Are you OK?

105
00:07:55,540 --> 00:07:57,140
Brother, what're you doing?

106
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:01,100
Brother,

107
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:02,820
where are you going?

108
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:05,340
You were knocked out a moment ago.

109
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:08,380
The pharmacist said you should rest well.

110
00:08:11,820 --> 00:08:12,460
Jielu,

111
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:15,580
you said I was knocked out?

112
00:08:15,900 --> 00:08:16,380
Right!

113
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:18,660
And you were knocked out by two people.

114
00:08:20,140 --> 00:08:21,700
Is my secret trip outside

115
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:22,860
the imperial palace exposed?

116
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:24,500
That I haven't heard of.

117
00:08:25,060 --> 00:08:26,820
However, for us inseparable king birds,

118
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:29,340
traditionally, unmarried men
are not allowed to leave the valley alone.

119
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:32,180
Brother, why do you break the rule repeatedly?

120
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:35,700
You know that I've longed for

121
00:08:35,860 --> 00:08:36,940
the colorful world outside the valley

122
00:08:37,420 --> 00:08:39,060
and wanted to experience the outside world for a long time.

123
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:41,900
I've waited so long for the Jiazi Valley to open,

124
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:44,060
but now it's all ruined.

125
00:08:44,100 --> 00:08:44,420
If...

126
00:08:45,380 --> 00:08:46,980
If Her Majesty finds out...

127
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:47,660
Well...

128
00:08:47,820 --> 00:08:48,620
So...

129
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:52,460
So I sneaked out.

130
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:54,020
Well,

131
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:57,380
where are the two people who knocked me out?

132
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:59,660
After hearing that they knocked you out,

133
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:01,820
Her Majesty ordered to put them into prison.

134
00:09:04,620 --> 00:09:06,300
Just let me finish.

135
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:08,860
Luckily, you're not severely injured,

136
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:11,220
so they've been sent to the water dungeon instead.

137
00:09:11,420 --> 00:09:12,500
I was the one who made the mistake.

138
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:14,060
I certainly can't get them in trouble.

139
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:17,140
Jielu, do you who knocked me out?

140
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:19,540
I only know it's a man and a woman.

141
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:21,820
Brother,

142
00:09:22,060 --> 00:09:23,420
wait for me!

143
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:47,260
Get out!

144
00:09:55,420 --> 00:09:57,060
Where're you taking me?

145
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:57,940
The water dungeon.

146
00:09:58,380 --> 00:09:59,180
The water dungeon?

147
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:01,780
You birds do have many tricks.

148
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:02,900
Cut the crap!

149
00:10:03,980 --> 00:10:05,940
Still feeling dizzy after falling down just now,

150
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:06,940
I don't feel like having a fight.

151
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:09,260
Otherwise, you wouldn't be able to capture me.

152
00:10:11,180 --> 00:10:13,300
Knocking out the prince of the inseparable king birds

153
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:14,620
can either be big or small.

154
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:16,180
If he can't wake up,

155
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:17,260
it's a big deal.

156
00:10:17,660 --> 00:10:18,580
If he wakes up,

157
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:19,620
with others interceding for us,

158
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:21,340
there's hope.

159
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:22,940
Hurry up! Hurry up!

160
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:30,580
Her Majesty ordered

161
00:10:30,820 --> 00:10:32,420
to escort them to the Palace Hall immediately.

162
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:35,780
It seems that he has woken up.

163
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:47,900
I just heard from the Second Prince that

164
00:10:48,300 --> 00:10:50,220
you're the prince and princess of

165
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:52,500
the night owls across the river.

166
00:10:53,540 --> 00:10:56,340
Admiring the Imperial College of our clan,

167
00:10:56,580 --> 00:10:58,300
you took a study tour here.

168
00:10:58,940 --> 00:11:00,780
You injured the Second Prince by accident.

169
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:10,260
Why did the Second Prince make up such a lie?

170
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:13,820
It appears that it's a misunderstanding after all.

171
00:11:14,020 --> 00:11:15,620
Sorry for making you suffer.

172
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:18,380
You're honored guests coming from afar.

173
00:11:18,740 --> 00:11:19,340
Well,

174
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:21,460
we should treat you well.

175
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:22,700
Thank you, Your Majesty!

176
00:11:24,780 --> 00:11:25,660
Thank you, Your Majesty!

177
00:11:26,420 --> 00:11:29,500
Since you admire our Imperial College,

178
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:31,940
I'll allow you to live in the Jifeng Courtyard of

179
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:34,180
the Imperial College.

180
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:37,180
On the one hand, your sincere wish

181
00:11:37,220 --> 00:11:39,060
to study in the Imperial College can be satisfied.

182
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:42,260
On the other hand, it's convenient
for younger generations of our two clans

183
00:11:42,380 --> 00:11:43,660
to exchange and compete with each other.

184
00:11:44,260 --> 00:11:45,900
What do you think?

185
00:11:46,260 --> 00:11:48,420
Your Majesty, thank you for your careful
and considerate arrangement.

186
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:50,060
We can't thank you enough.

187
00:11:50,180 --> 00:11:51,780
We'll definitely study hard in the Imperial College.

188
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:00,180
Mother,

189
00:12:01,380 --> 00:12:03,620
then I'll take them to the Jifeng Courtyard.

190
00:12:04,100 --> 00:12:04,700
Go ahead.

191
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:06,820
Please.

192
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:15,500
Let's go!

193
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:17,100
Go!

194
00:12:40,220 --> 00:12:42,340
Wait outside.

195
00:12:42,940 --> 00:12:43,340
Yes!

196
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:47,500
Your Highness, thank you for saving us on the hall just now.

197
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:49,860
But there's one thing we really can't understand.

198
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:51,100
Are you wondering

199
00:12:51,260 --> 00:12:52,740
why I saved you?

200
00:12:54,780 --> 00:12:55,420
Frankly speaking,

201
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:57,940
it's also for my own good.

202
00:12:58,980 --> 00:12:59,980
You mean?

203
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:02,340
I went out of the valley without permission.

204
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,660
If my mother finds out,

205
00:13:03,940 --> 00:13:05,060
she won't spare me easily.

206
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:06,260
But now,

207
00:13:06,380 --> 00:13:07,900
you're safe,

208
00:13:08,220 --> 00:13:09,500
and I can avoid being punished.

209
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:11,940
Please keep the secret for me.

210
00:13:12,780 --> 00:13:13,780
Your Highness, rest assured.

211
00:13:14,340 --> 00:13:14,900
However,

212
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:16,660
when can we get out of the valley?

213
00:13:16,940 --> 00:13:18,900
I'm afraid you'll have to wait for another 60 years.

214
00:13:19,180 --> 00:13:20,060
60 years!

215
00:13:20,260 --> 00:13:21,300
It's so long!

216
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:24,060
It's a long story.

217
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:27,300
We inseparable king birds

218
00:13:27,420 --> 00:13:28,740
are born fragile and delicate.

219
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:32,300
A tiny bit of foul air in the mortal realm can make us sick.

220
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:33,100
Therefore,

221
00:13:33,340 --> 00:13:34,740
many years ago, our ancestors

222
00:13:34,900 --> 00:13:37,220
found the Fanyin Valley after untold hardships

223
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:39,860
and led our entire clan to live a reclusive life in the valley.

224
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:42,900
Does this have anything to do with us leaving the valley?

225
00:13:43,820 --> 00:13:44,460
Take it easy.

226
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:45,660
I haven't finished yet.

227
00:13:46,180 --> 00:13:48,580
There's foul air sealed at the core of our valley.

228
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:49,940
If we open the valley too often,

229
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:51,540
the foul air might leak.

230
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:53,540
Once the Fanyin Valley is polluted,

231
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:55,780
the Four Seas and Eight Deserts will be in danger.

232
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:58,940
So the Fanyin Valley only opens every 60 years,

233
00:13:59,380 --> 00:14:01,060
and it only opens a crack

234
00:14:01,420 --> 00:14:02,300
for a short period of time, so that

235
00:14:02,540 --> 00:14:04,020
immortal messengers from the Sky Kingdom

236
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:05,420
on business to the valley can pass.

237
00:14:05,780 --> 00:14:08,700
The day you fell down
happens to be the opening date of the valley.

238
00:14:10,580 --> 00:14:11,100
Well,

239
00:14:11,260 --> 00:14:12,860
is there any other way to get out?

240
00:14:13,180 --> 00:14:15,740
Even the most perceptive immortal messenger from heaven

241
00:14:16,940 --> 00:14:18,020
needs to practice for three thousand years

242
00:14:18,340 --> 00:14:20,020
to pass that crack.

243
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:22,940
So long...

244
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:25,060
Take it easy.

245
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:27,820
Fate had us meet each other this way.

246
00:14:28,420 --> 00:14:29,380
I'm Xiang Limeng.

247
00:14:29,740 --> 00:14:31,780
I wonder what your names are.

248
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:33,980
You can call me Xiaojiu.

249
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:35,620
Xiaojiu?

250
00:14:35,980 --> 00:14:36,540
Terrific!

251
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:38,900
The princess of the night owls whose identity you've borrowed

252
00:14:39,100 --> 00:14:40,060
also has "Jiu" in her name.

253
00:14:40,220 --> 00:14:40,980
She's named Jiuge.

254
00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:43,740
It'll be convenient for you

255
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:44,620
to use her name in the Fanyin Valley later.

256
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:46,780
Then I'll call you Jiuge.

257
00:14:46,980 --> 00:14:48,300
OK! Good!

258
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:51,220
The Jifeng Courtyard has two rooms,
the east room and the west room.

259
00:14:51,660 --> 00:14:52,900
Feel relieved to live here.

260
00:14:53,060 --> 00:14:55,100
Whatever you need, just tell the servants.

261
00:14:55,660 --> 00:14:57,180
Your Highness, you're really considerate.

262
00:14:57,660 --> 00:14:58,780
Just call me Meng.

263
00:15:00,460 --> 00:15:02,740
Bro, I wonder how I should address you.

264
00:15:06,380 --> 00:15:07,540
Warrior Yan!

265
00:15:10,860 --> 00:15:12,420
Just call me Yan.

266
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:13,900
Jiuge. Yan.

267
00:15:14,260 --> 00:15:15,460
Have a good rest then.

268
00:15:15,820 --> 00:15:17,460
I'm leaving.

269
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:22,100
I'll take the east room.

270
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:23,540
You can have the west room.

271
00:15:27,140 --> 00:15:27,940
It's weird.

272
00:15:28,540 --> 00:15:29,820
After entering the Fanyin Valley,

273
00:15:29,940 --> 00:15:31,060
he seems infatuated.

274
00:15:31,420 --> 00:15:32,300
What's wrong with him?

275
00:15:47,740 --> 00:15:48,540
Get up!

276
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:50,700
What's wrong with you?

277
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:51,980
Get up now!

278
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:54,220
It's late at night! Why should I get up

279
00:15:54,380 --> 00:15:55,380
instead of sleeping?

280
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:56,500
We've been trapped in the valley

281
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:58,140
for so long.

282
00:15:58,300 --> 00:15:59,340
Rather than sit here and wait,

283
