00:28:34,220 --> 00:28:35,300
this tournament?

571
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:37,780
Those signing up this year

572
00:28:37,940 --> 00:28:39,420
are so excited because of the prize.

573
00:28:39,700 --> 00:28:40,820
What's the prize?

574
00:28:41,300 --> 00:28:42,540
It's the pimpon fruit.

575
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:44,420
The pimpon fruit?

576
00:28:44,940 --> 00:28:47,180
There is a kind of tree named pimpon,

577
00:28:47,820 --> 00:28:48,580
which blossoms once every ten years

578
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:49,740
and bears fruits once every ten years.

579
00:28:50,340 --> 00:28:51,460
According to the age of the tree,

580
00:28:51,660 --> 00:28:53,620
the fruits can have different uses.

581
00:28:54,020 --> 00:28:55,380
Fruits of certain age

582
00:28:55,540 --> 00:28:57,860
can not only make a mortal back to life,

583
00:28:58,060 --> 00:29:00,460
but can also turn a mortal into an immortal.

584
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:02,140
Isn't that the pimpon fruit

585
00:29:02,140 --> 00:29:02,980
which can save Ye Qingti?

586
00:29:03,540 --> 00:29:05,220
Jiuge, what did you say?

587
00:29:06,020 --> 00:29:06,740
I mean

588
00:29:06,940 --> 00:29:09,180
I've heard that

589
00:29:09,380 --> 00:29:10,500
the pimpon fruit is really rare.

590
00:29:10,660 --> 00:29:11,780
The pimpon tree blooms every ten years

591
00:29:11,980 --> 00:29:12,980
and bears fruits every ten years.

592
00:29:13,180 --> 00:29:14,740
Moreover, each tree can only bear one fruit.

593
00:29:15,100 --> 00:29:17,140
The effects of these fruits are different

594
00:29:17,180 --> 00:29:17,900
according to their harvest time.

595
00:29:18,420 --> 00:29:19,420
It's so precious!

596
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:20,900
So it is!

597
00:29:21,380 --> 00:29:23,500
The pimpon tree used to be

598
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:24,580
one of the five magic trees in the Sky Kingdom.

599
00:29:25,100 --> 00:29:25,940
Somehow,

600
00:29:26,140 --> 00:29:27,500
these trees all stopped bearing fruits.

601
00:29:27,700 --> 00:29:28,820
Now in heaven and on earth,

602
00:29:29,020 --> 00:29:31,580
only the pimpon tree beside the Jieyou Spring
inside the Fanyin Valley can bear fruits.

603
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:34,020
Well,

604
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:36,540
what's the effect of this pimpon fruit?

605
00:29:38,780 --> 00:29:39,980
I heard that as to the fruit this year,

606
00:29:40,380 --> 00:29:42,140
for mortals, it can add flesh to bones

607
00:29:42,300 --> 00:29:43,620
and resurrect the dead,

608
00:29:44,060 --> 00:29:45,820
and for immortals, it can improve cultivation

609
00:29:46,020 --> 00:29:47,300
and maintain youth and beauty forever.

610
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:49,620
Compared to the peach in the Sky Kingdom,

611
00:29:49,820 --> 00:29:50,940
it's far better.

612
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:54,220
Add flesh to bones and resurrect the dead.

613
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:55,100
Right.

614
00:29:55,660 --> 00:29:57,620
The bones can also be turned into an immortal body.

615
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:00,580
Then I'll go and sign up.

616
00:30:01,260 --> 00:30:01,780
Jiuge,

617
00:30:02,220 --> 00:30:03,660
it only works on mortals.

618
00:30:03,860 --> 00:30:04,540
As an immortal,

619
00:30:04,700 --> 00:30:05,340
it won't work on you.

620
00:30:05,820 --> 00:30:06,700
Didn't you just say

621
00:30:06,900 --> 00:30:09,340
by eating it, immortals can maintain youth and beauty forever?

622
00:30:11,380 --> 00:30:12,300
I see.

623
00:30:12,740 --> 00:30:13,300
However,

624
00:30:13,620 --> 00:30:15,700
the students signing up this year are more than ever.

625
00:30:16,340 --> 00:30:17,020
Due to limited competition place,

626
00:30:17,220 --> 00:30:19,140
my mother has ordered Master to screen the candidates in advance.

627
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:20,500
Only by passing his test

628
00:30:20,980 --> 00:30:22,260
can the candidates get to the final.

629
00:30:23,260 --> 00:30:24,660
To be screened by Master.

630
00:30:26,100 --> 00:30:26,340
Well,

631
00:30:27,180 --> 00:30:29,260
I've offended him repeatedly.

632
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:31,660
He won't let me get to the final for sure.

633
00:30:32,740 --> 00:30:35,020
Jiuge, what're you murmuring about?

634
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:35,740
Nothing.

635
00:30:35,940 --> 00:30:37,260
I said I have to go and sign up.

636
00:30:49,980 --> 00:30:51,020
The pimpon fruit?

637
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:56,060
It's extremely good

638
00:30:57,140 --> 00:30:58,420
for neutralizing my dark energy.

639
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:17,820
If the pimpon fruit can really resurrect the dead,

640
00:31:18,860 --> 00:31:21,380
Qingti, I'll definitely save you.

641
00:31:26,140 --> 00:31:27,460
I know you've got nothing good for me.

642
00:31:27,860 --> 00:31:29,100
You've followed the bad example of the ice face.

643
00:31:29,300 --> 00:31:30,620
Now you even smile as wickedly as he is.

644
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:33,140
If you have the strength to yell,

645
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:34,860
you might as well copy more characters for me.

646
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:36,460
Remember to imitate my handwriting.

647
00:31:37,860 --> 00:31:39,180
You are really demanding!

648
00:31:42,340 --> 00:31:43,220
How come it's so thick?

649
00:31:43,700 --> 00:31:45,580
Didn't Master only punish you to copy the book for ten times?

650
00:31:47,940 --> 00:31:48,740
I've offended

651
00:31:48,900 --> 00:31:50,380
that local tyrant.

652
00:31:50,860 --> 00:31:51,340
Also,

653
00:31:51,540 --> 00:31:52,660
in order to join the competition,

654
00:31:52,820 --> 00:31:53,740
I can take temporary setbacks

655
00:31:53,940 --> 00:31:55,140
to curry favor with him. Is that OK?

656
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:56,500
He asked me to copy the book for ten times.

657
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:57,580
I'll copy it for twenty times.

658
00:31:58,020 --> 00:31:59,540
I'm kind of trying to please him.

659
00:32:01,220 --> 00:32:03,740
Isn't it too implicit?

660
00:32:05,660 --> 00:32:06,180
Really?

661
00:32:09,900 --> 00:32:12,940
May Master Ji Han

662
00:32:13,660 --> 00:32:15,580
live a long and happy life.

663
00:32:17,380 --> 00:32:19,460
May Mater Ji Han

664
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:20,860
live a blessed and prosperous life.

665
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,700
What do you think? Will this please him?

666
00:32:23,420 --> 00:32:24,940
If he doesn't feel like reading to the end,

667
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:26,140
you've wasted time writing these words.

668
00:32:27,860 --> 00:32:28,540
Well,

669
00:32:28,740 --> 00:32:30,780
then I'll put the disgusting flattery

670
00:32:30,820 --> 00:32:31,700
in front.

671
00:32:31,860 --> 00:32:32,740
What do you think?

672
00:32:33,380 --> 00:32:34,060
I think it's OK.

673
00:32:36,780 --> 00:32:37,380
Wait!

674
00:32:38,140 --> 00:32:39,780
What on earth is his name?

675
00:32:39,980 --> 00:32:41,220
Ji Han or Han Ji?

676
00:32:42,260 --> 00:32:43,940
Isn't he called "Master"?

677
00:32:44,100 --> 00:32:45,740
Does he have another name?

678
00:32:57,860 --> 00:32:58,380
Your Majesty,

679
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:00,580
why do you summon me late at night?

680
00:33:02,700 --> 00:33:03,940
It's for the Miaoyi Chasm.

681
00:33:20,980 --> 00:33:22,140
Your Majesty, thanks to your righteousness,

682
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:24,060
after secluding yourself for seven days and seven nights,

683
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:25,580
you created the Miaoyi Chasm

684
00:33:26,060 --> 00:33:27,940
at the cost of your own cultivation,

685
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:30,660
thus keeping the mortal realm safe
for hundreds of thousands of years.

686
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:39,140
Judged from Your Majesty's look,

687
00:33:39,540 --> 00:33:41,740
is there anything wrong with the Miaoyi Chasm?

688
00:33:42,100 --> 00:33:45,420
The Miaoyi Chasm quaked three hundred years ago.

689
00:33:46,420 --> 00:33:49,220
I took many days to mend it,

690
00:33:49,620 --> 00:33:51,020
only to postpone

691
00:33:51,180 --> 00:33:52,380
its collapse.

692
00:33:53,100 --> 00:33:54,540
How long can it last?

693
00:33:55,140 --> 00:33:55,980
I don't know, either.

694
00:33:58,340 --> 00:33:59,260
I invite you over

695
00:33:59,980 --> 00:34:01,580
to work out a strategy.

696
00:34:02,220 --> 00:34:03,540
If the Miaoyi Chasm collapses,

697
00:34:04,340 --> 00:34:05,860
it will be a disaster for all men and gods.

698
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:08,980
It's a life-and-death matter of heaven and earth.

699
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:10,580
We must consider carefully before making a decision.

700
00:34:11,020 --> 00:34:11,580
Exactly.

701
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:25,620
Ever-victorious General,

702
00:34:26,180 --> 00:34:28,980
why are you so dispirited with your head down?

703
00:34:29,980 --> 00:34:34,060
Are you missing Her Highness Fengjiu from Qingqiu?

704
00:34:36,740 --> 00:34:38,140
Just like me.

705
00:34:55,180 --> 00:34:56,620
Take good care of it.

706
00:34:57,020 --> 00:34:57,620
Yes!

707
00:35:06,700 --> 00:35:07,260
Meng!

708
00:35:14,140 --> 00:35:14,780
Jiuge,

709
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:17,420
can you be more ladylike?

710
00:35:17,900 --> 00:35:19,140
Can you walk like a lady?

711
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:20,420
What's wrong with the way I walk?

712
00:35:20,620 --> 00:35:21,860
I do walk like a lady.

713
00:35:24,460 --> 00:35:24,940
Forget it.

714
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:27,340
What can I do for you?

715
00:35:29,300 --> 00:35:29,820
Meng,

716
00:35:30,300 --> 00:35:32,500
do you know the name of Master?

717
00:35:33,340 --> 00:35:34,060
Master?

718
00:35:36,020 --> 00:35:37,420
Why do you suddenly ask me this?

719
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:41,180
You must have thought of a prank.

720
00:35:42,140 --> 00:35:43,300
What're you talking about?

721
00:35:43,500 --> 00:35:45,060
Am I so mischievous?

722
00:35:46,220 --> 00:35:48,900
Do you know it or not?

723
00:35:49,380 --> 00:35:53,700
I actually don't know his real name.

724
00:35:54,060 --> 00:35:56,100
I've called him "Master" since childhood.

725
00:35:57,740 --> 00:35:58,940
It's weird.

726
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:00,940
How come his name

727
00:36:00,940 --> 00:36:02,340
is even more confidential

728
00:36:02,460 --> 00:36:03,260
than a girl's name?

729
00:36:03,780 --> 00:36:04,580
I don't believe that

730
00:36:04,780 --> 00:36:06,100
no one

731
00:36:06,220 --> 00:36:07,100
in the entire Imperial College

732
00:36:07,100 --> 00:36:08,100
knows his name!

733
00:36:08,660 --> 00:36:09,140
Just wait!

734
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:10,860
I'll ask whoever I see later.

735
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:12,300
I can definitely get his name.

736
00:36:13,820 --> 00:36:16,140
Wish you good luck!

737
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:25,300
Your Majesty,

738
00:36:25,580 --> 00:36:28,140
Immortal Official Chong Lin, the Chief Immortal Messenger
of Tai Chen Palace has sent the word that

739
00:36:28,380 --> 00:36:29,660
the tea class scheduled tomorrow

740
00:36:29,740 --> 00:36:31,940
will be taught by another immortal official.

741
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:35,660
Busy as immortal official is,

742
00:36:35,900 --> 00:36:38,620
we feel honored that he's willing to give a lecture in our clan.

743
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:42,980
Inform the Master. Ask him to arrange it properly.

744
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:44,380
Yes.

745
00:37:09,180 --> 00:37:10,260
Isn't that His Majesty?

746
00:37:10,500 --> 00:37:10,980
Yes.

747
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:13,140
Since His Majesty is gonna give the lecture

748
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:17,100
in the Fanyin Valley as usual,

749
00:37:17,620 --> 00:37:21,340
why do you ask me to give the lecture about tea on his behalf?

750
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:22,780
Here's the thing.

751
00:37:23,140 --> 00:37:25,500
Last night, His Majesty and His Highness Lian Song
discussed something important.

752
00:37:25,740 --> 00:37:27,060
I thought he wouldn't come,

753
00:37:27,260 --> 00:37:28,980
so I asked you to give the lecture on his behalf as usual.

754
00:37:31,100 --> 00:37:32,580
I didn't expect

755
00:37:32,620 --> 00:37:33,980
His Majesty would come.

756
00:37:34,900 --> 00:37:36,780
With the Eight Deserts and Six Directions to be concerned about,

757
00:37:37,020 --> 00:37:39,220
His Majesty even remembers to give a lecture.

758
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:42,540
The world is so blessed to have him as the emperor.

759
00:37:44,020 --> 00:37:44,820
Your Excellency, sorry for bothering you.

760
00:37:45,060 --> 00:37:46,180
Now that His Majesty is here in person,

761
00:37:46,380 --> 00:37:48,060
Your Excellency may as well go back to the Sky Kingdom.

762
00:37:49,420 --> 00:37:50,060
See you.

763
00:37:59,700 --> 00:38:02,740
His Majesty didn't ask me to accompany him this time.

764
00:38:03,260 --> 00:38:04,340
He actually went there alone.

765
00:38:05,060 --> 00:38:05,780
Is he not here

766
00:38:07,220 --> 00:38:08,580
for the Miaoyi Chasm?

767
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:20,780
OK. OK. OK.

768
00:38:22,380 --> 00:38:22,900
Hurry up! Hurry up!

769
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:23,460
That's all?

770
00:38:23,700 --> 00:38:24,020
Yes.

771
00:38:37,020 --> 00:38:37,740
Princess Jielu,

772
00:38:38,420 --> 00:38:40,060
I wonder why you set

773
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:41,020
these traps.

774
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:41,620
Right.

775
00:38:41,820 --> 00:38:43,260
Haven't you heard Master yesterday?

776
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:44,340
Today, an immortal official

777
00:38:44,540 --> 00:38:46,740
good at tea theories will give a lecture about tea instead.

778
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:48,820
I want to use these traps

779
00:38:49,020 --> 00:38:50,260
to scare him away.

780
00:38:50,860 --> 00:38:52,540
But if he's scared away,

781
00:38:52,860 --> 00:38:55,020
no one will give us the lecture.

782
00:38:55,220 --> 00:38:56,740
That's exactly what I want.

783
00:38:57,020 --> 00:38:58,020
In that way,

784
00:38:58,020 --> 00:38:59,020
the lecture can be given by the original master.

785
00:38:59,100 --> 00:38:59,460
Right!

786
00:39:00,420 --> 00:39:01,460
Your Highness, you're so clever.

787
00:39:02,980 --> 00:39:03,780
Clever?

788
00:39:04,260 --> 00:39:05,900
I find her too naive.

789
00:39:06,500 --> 00:39:08,220
I wonder who on earth

790
00:39:08,460 --> 00:39:09,180
that beloved and respected master is.

791
00:39:09,500 --> 00:39:09,980
Give me a hand.

792
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:31,740
I know you love him deeply,

793
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:33,660
but he pays no attention to you.

794
00:39:34,940 --> 00:39:36,580
You're as far apart as heaven and earth.

795
00:39:36,980 --> 00:39:38,060
By doing so,

796
00:39:38,580 --> 00:39:39,900
he might be annoyed

797
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:42,220
and may never give lectures in our clan again.

798
00:39:43,180 --> 00:39:44,700
It's fine if he stops giving lectures here.

799
00:39:45,380 --> 00:39:47,540
But if my mother wants to punish you for that,

800
00:39:47,980 --> 00:39:50,140
don't blame me for not interceding for you.

801
00:39:50,540 --> 00:39:51,860
If Her Majesty blames me,

802
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:52,740
I'll accept the punishment myself.

803
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:54,100
I don't need your help.

804
00:39:55,020 --> 00:39:56,060
Then do you know

805
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:57,900
he's got a lover

806
00:39:58,140 --> 00:39:59,420
in the Sky Kingdom.

807
00:39:59,780 --> 00:40:00,580
When did that happen?

808
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:02,060
How come I've never heard about it?

809
00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:06,500
I heard that though they haven't performed
the heaven-worshipping ritual,

810
00:40:07,180 --> 00:40:10,020
he treats that fairy as his wife.

811
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:12,540
He not only treasures and favors her,

812
00:40:13,780 --> 00:40:16,460
but sleeps and shares a bath with her.

813
00:40:22,660 --> 00:40:23,580
Why are you crying?

814
00:40:24,540 --> 00:40:26,500
Speaking of dandies in the Sky Kingdom,

815
00:40:27,140 --> 00:40:29,220
Lian Song, the Third Prince of the Heavenly King,
is the most famous.

816
00:40:29,700 --> 00:40:31,900
But I've heard nothing about him

817
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:34,860
sleeping and sharing a bath with a woman
before performing the heaven-worshipping ritual.

818
00:40:35,420 --> 00:40:37,580
Which immortal official on earth is so wild and absurd?

819
00:40:38,580 --> 00:40:40,260
It's quite impressive actually.

820
00:40:44,700 --> 00:40:45,780
Stop crying!

821
00:40:46,420 --> 00:40:48,660
I suck at dealing with girl's tears.

822
00:40:51,020 --> 00:40:51,940
If you stop crying,

823
00:40:52,220 --> 00:40:54,020
I'll help you set the trap, OK?

824
00:40:54,940 --> 00:40:56,540
I'll also cover for you in front of my mother.

825
00:40:56,740 --> 00:40:57,820
You said that on purpose.

826
00:40:58,100 --> 00:40:59,940
You love the Princess of Qingqiu secretly,

827
00:41:00,180 --> 00:41:00,900
but your love is not responded,

828
00:41:00,980 --> 00:41:02,900
so you hope that everyone in the world

829
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:03,820
can end up alone

830
00:41:04,020 --> 00:41:04,700
and unaccompanied like you are.

831
00:41:04,940 --> 00:41:05,740
Stop talking nonsense!

832
00:41:05,980 --> 00:41:07,180
You're the one who talked nonsense!

833
00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:08,860
Noble and unsullied as master is,

834
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:10,180
how could he do that?

835
00:41:10,660 --> 00:41:11,220
I don't believe you!

836
00:41:11,420 --> 00:41:12,660
Not a word!

837
00:41:16,140 --> 00:41:17,180
Why is Her Highness crying?

838
00:41:17,220 --> 00:41:17,740
Unbelievable!

839
00:41:18,140 --> 00:41:19,220
The Princess of Qingqiu?

840
00:41:20,660 --> 00:41:21,900
I didn't expect that in such a remote place,

841
00:41:21,940 --> 00:41:23,020
there's still a young man so dejected

842
00:41:23,660 --> 00:41:25,580
because of my aunt!

843
00:41:26,060 --> 00:41:26,820
Awesome!

844
00:41:29,100 --> 00:41:29,580
Jiuge,

845
00:41:32,220 --> 00:41:32,620
